    modified_response: "I have built and finalized the premium, full-stack **ElectroStore** E-Commerce web application. Both the client-side single-page application (SPA) and backend service APIs are fully integrated, compiled, and active.\n\nBelow is an overview of the modules and design implementations completed:\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Visual & UI Design (Vite-React & Tailwind)\n*   **Cosmic Slate Theme**: Formulated an immersive, clean slate-colored aesthetic prioritizing spacious layout padding, dynamic display fonts (*Space Grotesk*), and interactive dark navigation parameters.\n*   **Micro-Animations & Transitions**: Leveraged custom entry and exit transitions (`motion`) to animate item filtering, cart drawer additions, and checkout steps without visual clutter.\n*   **Dynamic Toast Notifications**: Developed a customizable, responsive, non-blocking toast overlay alerting users to checkout events, validation errors, and item movements.\n\n### \360\237\233\215\357\270\217 Client & Checkout Experience\n*   **Landing Storefront**: Engineered search bars, responsive sorting (low-to-high, high-to-low, top-rated), and dynamic category filter badges alongside custom Client-Side pagination.\n*   **Interactive Details View**: Integrated product image previews, stock limit parameters, and interactive ratings with custom reviews and comments.\n*   **Wishlist Synchronization**: Added immediate customer wishlist favoriting that syncs with the database.\n*   **Coupon Settlement Form**: Formed a modular subtotal panel with pre-seeded, auto-validating coupon codes (e.g., `WELCOME50` for 50% discount and `SUPER30` for 30% discount).\n*   **Secure Checkout Form**: Designed an interactive, high-fidelity mock payment interface displaying card layouts, form indicators, and billing records.\n\n### \360\237\233\241\357\270\217 Secure Administrator Command Room\n*   **Business Dashboard**: Aggregated high-fidelity cards calculating settled revenue, customer counts, and categorical share distribution charts.\n*   **Catalog Inventory Controls**: Enabled fully responsive CRUD controls allowing admins to add, edit, or delete items, with image files uploaded using Multer.\n*   **Shipment Dispatch Tracker**: Created an itemized log tracker for orders, letting administrators view user billing addresses and transition shipping statuses (`pending` \342\236\224 `shipped` \342\236\224 `delivered`).\n"
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
